                      CENTRAL ASSET INVESTMENTS & MANAGEMENT HOLDINGS (HK) LTD
                    

•   HONG KONG, K3
                      
How do I update this listing?




                                             Central Asset Investments & Management Holdings (hk) LTD is based out of Hong Kong.   Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $189,734,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 88.45%. Central Asset Investments & Management Holdings (hk) LTD's largest holding is Ctrip.Com International Ltd ADS with shares held of 25,600,000.   WhaleWisdom has at least 18 13F filings in our database for Central Asset Investments & Management Holdings (hk) LTD. 
                                           














