Arena Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (ARNA) Analysts See $-0.68 EPS; Central Asset Investments & Management Holdings Hk LTD Upped By $1.37 Million Its Netease (NTES) Holding

July 25, 2017 - By Hazel Jackson


 Analysts expect Arena Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (NASDAQ:ARNA) to report $-0.68 EPS on August, 14.They anticipate $0.42 EPS change or 38.18% from last quarter’s $-1.1 EPS. After having $-0.90 EPS previously, Arena Pharmaceuticals, Inc.’s analysts see -24.44% EPS growth. About 401,290 shares traded. Arena Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (NASDAQ:ARNA) has declined 11.92% since July 25, 2016 and is downtrending. It has underperformed by 28.62% the S&P500.
Central Asset Investments & Management Holdings Hk Ltd increased Netease Inc (NTES) stake by 92.17% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Central Asset Investments & Management Holdings Hk Ltd acquired 6,360 shares as Netease Inc (NTES)’s stock declined 3.53%. The Central Asset Investments & Management Holdings Hk Ltd holds 13,260 shares with $2.86M value, up from 6,900 last quarter. Netease Inc now has $41.11B valuation. The stock declined 0.83% or $2.6 reaching $308.9 on the news. About 468,251 shares traded. NetEase Inc (ADR) (NASDAQ:NTES) has risen 77.85% since July 25, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 61.15% the S&P500.






Central Asset Investments & Management Holdings Hk Ltd decreased Alibaba Group Hldg Ltd (NYSE:BABA) stake by 214,976 shares to 18,324 valued at $1.61 million in 2016Q4. It also reduced Facebook Inc (NASDAQ:FB) stake by 21,000 shares and now owns 2,600 shares. Trina Solar Limited (NYSE:TSL) was reduced too. 
Among 14 analysts covering NetEase (NASDAQ:NTES), 10 have Buy rating, 3 Sell and 1 Hold. Therefore 71% are positive. NetEase had 27 analyst reports since August 12, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. The company was downgraded on Friday, October 16 by Standpoint Research. The firm has “Buy” rating by Jefferies given on Friday, June 16. The firm has “Outperform” rating given on Monday, September 21 by Credit Suisse. The stock of NetEase Inc (ADR) (NASDAQ:NTES) earned “Hold” rating by Standpoint Research on Wednesday, August 26. Credit Suisse initiated the shares of NTES in report on Friday, August 19 with “Neutral” rating. Nomura initiated the stock with “Neutral” rating in Friday, January 22 report. The firm has “Buy” rating given on Wednesday, November 25 by Goldman Sachs. The stock of NetEase Inc (ADR) (NASDAQ:NTES) has “Hold” rating given on Thursday, September 29 by Jefferies. The firm earned “Buy” rating on Monday, January 9 by Standpoint Research. JP Morgan maintained NetEase Inc (ADR) (NASDAQ:NTES) on Thursday, February 25 with “Overweight” rating.
Since May 12, 2017, it had 1 buying transaction, and 0 selling transactions for $29,750 activity. On Friday, May 12 the insider Munshi Amit bought $29,750.
Investors sentiment increased to 1.97 in 2016 Q4. Its up 0.79, from 1.18 in 2016Q3. It is positive, as 9 investors sold Arena Pharmaceuticals, Inc. shares while 25 reduced holdings. 19 funds opened positions while 48 raised stakes. 110.93 million shares or 6.74% less from 118.95 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Massachusetts-based Camber Capital Mngmt Llc has invested 0.31% in Arena Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (NASDAQ:ARNA). Alliancebernstein Lp holds 434,153 shares. Goldman Sachs Incorporated reported 546,781 shares. Ascend Llc reported 0.13% stake. Raymond James Financial Ser Advisors invested 0% in Arena Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (NASDAQ:ARNA). Horizon Kinetics Lc reported 0% of its portfolio in Arena Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (NASDAQ:ARNA). Teacher Retirement System Of Texas holds 0% or 19,678 shares. 30,528 are held by Commerzbank Aktiengesellschaft Fi. The Kansas-based Creative Planning has invested 0% in Arena Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (NASDAQ:ARNA). Next Fincl Group invested in 5,054 shares. The California-based Schwab Charles Inv Management has invested 0% in Arena Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (NASDAQ:ARNA). Blackrock Fund Advsrs holds 0% or 11.23M shares. Ny State Common Retirement Fund reported 220,800 shares stake. 60,600 are owned by Invesco Ltd. Jfs Wealth Ltd Liability Com owns 740 shares.



